Title:
3.0 out of 5 stars
An ordinary watch but is fine considering the price.
Review:
I purchased it for Rs. 349 on festival sale. The printed price is Rs.2199.Pros-1. The material used is fine.2. The watch dial is large. So watching the time is easy.3. The dates of 2 days before and after the present day are shown.4. The day is also shown.5. The holes on the strap give the luxury of reducing or increasing the size of the strap according to the wrist size of the wearer.6. The key used to change the time, day and date is also big enough to operate comfortably.7. Cheap.Cons-1. The strap material is not good.2. The looks are not that good as shown in the product picture.Final comment- If you are short on the budget then only go for it. It is good value for money but if you have a good budget, stay away from this watch.
